    <div class="container">
        <img src="purposing scene.png" alt="Valentine's Day Couple" class="header-image">
        <h1>üíñ Will you be my friend? üíñ</h1>
        <p>Will you be my friend in this Valentine ? I've been thinking about you a lot, and I can't imagine a better way to spend Valentine's Day than with you. What do you say?</p>
        <div class="images">
            <!-- Lovely Valentine's Day Pictures of Proposing -->
            <img src="hinata naruto.jpg" alt="Romantic Proposal">
